name: The Terrible Dancer
description: The world collapses as she dances. She left the world somewhere beyond her existence. She trades her soul in dancing, only to get hurt by the madness of the world. She tries to grow a sunflower in herself, because it holds the name of a greater power than the world, SUN, but she was wrong, the FLOWER was still a world invention. Yet, she still dances away, though it tears her apart, because she knows, she will be forever trapped in the square.
